name: ARCHETYPE_ID
title: ARCHETYPE_ID
description: Identifier for archetypes. Ideally these would identify globally unique archetypes. Lexical form: rm_originator '-' rm_name '-' rm_entity '.' concept_name { '-' specialisation }* '.v' number.
